You are currently hosting this on Pagodabox
To push to Pagodabox, you need to add the remote (check documentation), push --all
You need to have an SSH key between Pagodabox and your git installation. This can be generated (check pagoda's documentation) and added
Files in:
data
conf
lib/plugins
are all in shared writable directories
These are not handled by the git push, so when there is an update to the wiki on either side, there needs to be a git reconciliation AND a ssh sharable directory reconciliation.
Conflicts will not be handled easily, so only modify one at a time, and always reconcile after writing